    Overview

    Create templates for frequently used messages and apply them on any web page, platform or service!

    Templify saves time for users who communicate frequently and is ideal for small businesses, customer service teams, recruiters, and salespeople. This messaging automation tool has proven to be effective, with over 2,000 active users and 5-star reviews! What makes Templify Extension the top choice for daily use? Works Everywhere: Apply message templates on any website, platform, or service without limitations. Templify fits seamlessly into any business process! Easy to Use: No need to remember shortcuts or switch to an external app. Create, browse, and apply message templates right where you work exactly when you need them! Helpful Features: Supercharge your workflow with smart syntax, organized template groups, shared team workspaces, lightning-fast keyboard controls, and more. Templify doesnt require unnecessary permissions like many other extensions. It respects your privacy and follows the best privacy practices. Achieve more with a fast and consistent workflow! Templify Extension helps users save time and streamline any writing or communication process increasing productivity and improving customer engagement. Small businesses and customer service teams use Templify to create templates for product or service details and responses to frequently asked questions such as delivery, payment, or return information. Its widely used for efficient customer communication across platforms like Amazon, eBay, Shopify, and more. Recruiters and talent sourcers create templates for connection requests, recruitment pitches, and job descriptions, which can be used on LinkedIn or in web-based messengers. Recruiters often use smart syntax to personalize messages and increase candidate engagement. Sales professionals and SDRs build templates for every stage of the sales funnel and use them for social selling on LinkedIn, X (Twitter), Facebook, and other platforms. Like recruiters, they rely on smart syntax to personalize outreach and improve response rates. Templify is also popular for storing and applying AI prompts including ChatGPT prompts, Midjourney prompts, Notion AI prompts, and more. Youll often find Templify listed as a LinkedIn messaging tool, HubSpot sales tool, recruiter tool, customer service tool, seller tool, or under related keywords such as canned responses, message templates, snippets, email templates, macros, auto-text, clipboard templates, and copy-paste text. Ready to give it a try? Get started for free (no credit card required) become more efficient and professional, and save time for what truly matters!
